Subject:
Fine Arts Club || Location sketching || October 2, 9 AM

Body:
Hello all,

Ever wanted to sketch the scenaries of Insti? Here is the chance..

FineArtsClub IITM and Chennai Weekend Artists collectively presents the
'Location Sketching' event on this sunday. Do participate and get to
interact with professional artists from the Chennai Weekend Artists group.

What is Location Sketching : Sitting in a location and sketching/ painting
what you see from the surrounding environment. 'SampleImages'


Materials provided will be : Pencils, color pencils, poster colors,
brushes, A3 & A4 sheets. Please bring a book or small wooden plank as a
support for the A4 sheet.

Date : 2nd October 2016.

Venue : CLT and surroundings

TIme : 9:00AM  12:30PM

 At the end of the event, everyone shall gather at CLT with your works,
where good points about the works and the suggestions will be discussed
among ourselves.

Check here to know more about Chennai weekend artists : CWApage
 , Event


Hoping to see you all tmrw at CLT..,

Cheers.

For quieries..

